    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 font-sans">What's in the guide</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-ink mb-8">
      <li><strong>Part 1 — Choosing the right app (pages 1-10)</strong> — decision framework for companion, mental-health, romance verticals</li>
      <li><strong>Part 2 — Setup &amp; first 30 days (pages 11-20)</strong> — character creation, memory seeding, tone calibration</li>
      <li><strong>Part 3 — Privacy-first configuration (pages 21-28)</strong> — opt-out training, data export, local memory if available</li>
      <li><strong>Part 4 — Advanced conversation (pages 29-36)</strong> — roleplay scenarios, emotional depth, long-term relationship arcs</li>
      <li><strong>Part 5 — Pitfalls &amp; mental-health boundaries (pages 37-40)</strong> — when to step back, crisis resources, real-world balance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 font-sans">Who this is for</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-ink mb-8">
      <li>New users evaluating Replika, Nomi, Kindroid, Candy.ai and similar</li>
      <li>Current users wanting to get deeper value from their subscription</li>
      <li>Privacy-conscious users wanting to lock down their setup</li>
      <li>NOT a substitute for mental-health professional care. See our <a href="/disclaimer-mental-health/" class="text-accent">disclaimer</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 font-sans">FAQ</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
      <div><strong>Is this a PDF or a subscription?</strong><br>One-time €19 payment. PDF download. No subscription, no renewal.</div>
      <div><strong>Can I get a refund?</strong><br>14-day refund via Gumroad, no questions asked.</div>
      <div><strong>Will this make me dependent on AI companion apps?</strong><br>Part 5 of the guide is explicitly about healthy boundaries and knowing when to step back. We include direct crisis resource contacts.</div>
      <div><strong>Is it updated?</strong><br>Free updates for 12 months after purchase (apps change often).</div>
    </div>

    <NewsletterForm compact />
  </section>
</Base>
